Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・『Ｃｒａｚｙ　Ｒａｉｎｂｏｗ』\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:01:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,・～\N
